snippet.title: "I Had An Affair With Amber" James Franco Speaks on Dating Her While She Was Married To Johnny Depp

"I Had An Affair With Amber" James Franco Speaks on Dating Her While She Was Married To Johnny Depp 
It looks like James Franco’s legal troubles aren’t going away anytime soon and that is just putting it lightly as his woes just keep mounting up.
And now, James has been served papers in the long-running legal battle between Johnny Depp and his estranged wife, Amber Heard. 
So some of you might be wondering, what exactly does James have to do with the Depp/Heard lawsuit?
